<div class="container title border">
  <h1 class="align-left-custom">Packtrack</h1>
  <span class="fa-stack align-right-custom">
    <a href="http://www.jonathantau.com">
      {{fa-icon "fa-square-o" stack=2}}
      {{fa-icon "fa-envelope" stack=1}}
    </a>
  </span>
</div>

<div class="container top-buffer">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 tracker-container">
    <br>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="carrier">Carrier:</label>
        {{view "select" prompt="Select a carrier" content=carriers value=selectedCarrier classNames="form-control"}}
        <br>
        <br>
        <label for="trackingNum">Tracking Number:</label>
        {{input type="text" value=trackingNum classNames="form-control"}}
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <button {{action "submit"}} class="btn btn-info">track!</button>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>About</h3>
        <p>This is a side project that I decided to work on. I often find myself looking up tracking information for different carriers, and thought that it would be really convenient to create a single landing page where I could lookup tracking information for different carriers. Initially this started out as a python CLI project, but I figured that it would be much more user friendly if I developed this as a web app. Feel free to visit my website by clicking the mail icon on the upper right hand corner.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


